parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system malfunctions
causing the speedometer
fuel gauge
and other instruments to fail
the radio and lights to turn on and off
and the airbags to deploy unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster can cause the driver to lose visibility of important vehicle information, such as speed, fuel level, and engine performance, leading to accidents or unsafe driving conditions.
symptoms: The instrument cluster fails
causing the speedometer
fuel gauge
oil pressure gauge
and other instruments to malfunction or fail completely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body sensor can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The throttle body sensor fails
causing the vehicle to stall or shut down
and the "Reduced Engine Power" light to illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the Passlock anti-theft system can cause the vehicle to shut down while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The Passlock anti-theft system malfunctions
causing the vehicle to shut down
and the fuel pump to fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake lines can cause the brake pedal to go to the floor, leading to a loss of braking power, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
brake fluid leaking from under the vehicle
rust or corrosion on the brake lines
sudden loss of braking power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the brake pedal to go to the floor, leading to a loss of braking power, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
sudden loss of braking power
brake fluid leaking from under the vehicle
rust or corrosion on the brake lines
warning lights on the dashboard.
